            <td width="550" align="center" valign="top" style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size:28px; color:#00aeef; line-height:32px; "><font face="century gothic"><strong>NCS – you have hours to make up before you can graduate</strong></td><BR>
            <td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
            <td width="600" height="20" colspan="3" align="center" valign="top"><img src="https://wolfegang.co.uk/hosting/the-challenge/2014/html-1/template02-hr-130114.jpg" width="600" height="20" style="display:block;" border="0" /></td>
